527
00:50:12.875 --> 00:50:16.208
Don't let them see you like this.
you're still Cap.

528
00:50:27.375 --> 00:50:28.666
That was a hike.

529
00:50:35.375 --> 00:50:37.083
Mr. Hairy! We want some too.

530
00:50:37.458 --> 00:50:38.541
